Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:06.44,Default,,0,0,100,,Are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a letter from my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:00:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,My best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.43,0:00:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was fifteen years old...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.34,0:00:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,we tried to cross the Czech border together.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.94,0:00:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She was caught and sent back to Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.18,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She knows me better than anyone in my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A true friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.92,0:00:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what kind of censorship\Nthis letter had to go through...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.29,0:00:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,before she could send it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"If we ever get a chance to meet again..."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"please come to this place...."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.60,0:00:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Cedok Bridge, the Three Frogs."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to go back... to Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.65,0:01:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.85,0:01:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.16,0:01:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me by my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.69,0:01:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for tonight, I'd like you to use my real name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.30,0:01:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Helenka Novakowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.74,0:01:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Just for tonight, I'm not Margot Langer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.73,0:03:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I sold my Reiser-Berger Pharmaceutical\Nstock in the nick of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.49,0:03:02.53,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(750,0)\pos(360,340)}The Monster's Love Letter
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I bought some Kneuter Research stock...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.64,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and I hit the jackpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.44,0:03:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just had to celebrate after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.34,0:03:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.71,0:03:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.68,0:03:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm appalled.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.32,0:03:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It was just one glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.12,0:03:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I've said this many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.25,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're an alcoholic...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't matter how much you drink, it's all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.76,0:03:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And you've been ditching the alcohol\Nrehab group I recommended for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.16,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.80,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, can you keep this secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is, there's a woman I want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Another one of your lovers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.54,0:03:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a really bad alcoholic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She's waiting right outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a quick look at her?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.82,0:03:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that without an appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.69,0:03:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Have one set up for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.89,0:04:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A quick look would be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.06,0:04:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a house call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.26,0:04:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,For a very important patient, at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Prague, in the Czech Republic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.80,0:04:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Prague Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The cathedrals, with their marvelous Gothic architecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The view of the old commercial district\Nat night was also stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was like I was in a fairyland.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.98,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And Cedok Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.88,0:04:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you go to Cedok Bridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, just as you asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it! The Three Frogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.70,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was the woman there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No one was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.10,0:04:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't find anything by going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.94,0:04:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma, Nina, and even Dieter...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't find anything that indicates where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.52,0:05:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.82,0:05:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rabbit's foot that brings good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for our child you're carrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot... no, Helenka...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.73,Title,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Prague, 1980
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.01,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:06:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come from Germany, and I'm\Ntrying to find a missing woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.05,0:06:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot Langer...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.22,0:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I mean Helenka Novakowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Helenka...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.06,0:06:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mr. Schuwald...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your son, karl, mentioned this to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.50,0:06:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't been eating again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that during the fire in the\NUniversity of Munich Library...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you experienced something truly terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,And I understand that you haven't overcome that fear yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.82,0:06:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you still have karl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,who is such a splendid son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.96,0:06:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to worry anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just eat properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.37,0:07:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as that monster exists, I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,How did that monster know so\Nmuch about Margot Langer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew more than my son did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Margot had a friend in Prague who knew\Nher better than her own family did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.86,0:07:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The woman she exchanged letters with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.76,0:07:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Around 1980...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.10,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,you went searching for the missing Margot...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.00,0:07:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and you met that woman in Prague.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she may have heard something from Margot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.38,0:07:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She hadn't heard anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.22,0:07:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We talked about Margot for a little while in her doorway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,they were listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,to our conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quietly listening...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.60,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,standing behind the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.51,0:08:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,They were twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a seat over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You were referred by Mr. Talbach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.69,0:08:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You also have drinking problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.46,0:08:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just have a casual conversation for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.46,0:08:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Mehres?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.76,0:08:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of a counseling session.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Just now, on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.73,0:08:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma! Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.17,0:08:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Czech police have just announced...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.81,0:08:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the capture of the main suspect in the poisoning...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.81,0:08:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}of three murdered doctors from Eisler Memorial{\i}\N{\i1}Hospital in Düsseldorf, Germany...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the murders of the journalist Mauler{\i}\N{\i1}and the Fortners in Heidelberg...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the street murder at Heidelberg Castle.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.42,0:08:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Japanese doctor, Kenzo Tenma,{\i}\N{\i1}who had been hiding in Prague....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was apprehended on the afternoon of the 5th.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're still waiting for more information on his arrest....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.30,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the details will be released later...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- during the police press conference....{\i}\N- Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.04,0:09:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come in here!\NThis is a private office...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so please wait in the other room, Ms. Eva Heinemann!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.48,0:09:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hess, you look ten years younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe because I've been taking\Ncare of my grandkids too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.89,0:09:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,How've you been, Hubert?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.86,0:09:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I somehow made it to my senior year...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.86,0:09:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kiefer, I heard you've been doing very well lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.80,0:09:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been bragging that I know a script writer\Nwho's been invited to Hollywood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I just happened to catch a producer's eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My mind's become very sharp...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.84,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and new ideas just keep pouring into my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.98,0:09:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.92,0:09:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since that surgery...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.15,0:10:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If that brain surgery hadn't been successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.26,0:10:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,right now, I'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.93,0:10:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able to take walks\Nin the park with my grandchildren.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.53,0:10:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That seat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.43,0:10:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He was always drinking tea by himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there were other cafés where doctors met...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,he always came to this one, in the\Nback of Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.81,0:10:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When we the patients, would come here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,he would look up from over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and wave at us with a smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a kind doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.86,0:10:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way a kind doctor like\Nhim could do something like this
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the reason I asked you to come today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, even the people who couldn't make it here\Ntoday must be feeling the same way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.60,0:10:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,if they were Dr. Tenma's former patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.34,0:10:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Schumann, we've got trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Old man Merkel collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.11,0:11:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.92,0:11:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in the middle of something right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.85,0:11:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but please wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.69,0:11:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma wouldn't have done such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.76,0:11:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down and listen, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.10,0:11:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, go to him, honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but Petra...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no "but"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.74,0:11:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma's been arrested for crimes he didn't commit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If not for him, I wouldn't be here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to pretend nothing happened,\Nwhen your wife's savior is in big trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.05,0:11:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the village?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.85,0:11:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,In this village, I'm the only doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If I leave, what's going to happen\Nto the people in this village?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't make excuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.80,0:11:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to go, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and go save Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.17,0:11:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When a doctor has patients, he cannot leave them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma would do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.37,0:12:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please hurry and see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.84,0:12:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepping right now, so wait there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you gonna make us wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.91,0:12:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.45,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,She's been going to medical school recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,She still runs an unauthorized clinic for us at her own risk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.33,0:12:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you stay in the darkness, you'll sink into the darkness...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.00,0:12:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shine light upon it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure, you can become a doctor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.74,0:12:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'll be a good doctor.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,First patient, please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.16,0:12:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But we still don't know where in Germany\NTenma will be transferred.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Pick a lawyer for each state...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.70,0:13:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The best criminal lawyers out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.94,0:13:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.94,0:13:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Only that man...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.68,0:13:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel only that man can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Only he can obliterate the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.45,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's gather more people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.72,0:13:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's call out to Dr. Tenma's former patients.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.29,0:13:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Alone, each of us may not have much\Ninfluence, but if we all pull together...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.10,0:13:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's ask Eisler Memorial for their cooperation...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and create a rescue association...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial won't help with that kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.24,0:13:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been listening to you for a little while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a tearjerker!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you guys going to prove Tenma's innocence?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.86,0:14:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Becker!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.89,0:14:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a motive, and no alibi at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard they also found material evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.77,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you get together and make a\Nfuss, or hire a competent lawyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.34,0:14:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,it's impossible to prove Tenma's innocence either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Such an eminent doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It's unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.76,0:14:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll ask you again, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.80,0:14:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of relationship do you have with Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.77,0:14:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know who you are, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to rescue Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.54,0:14:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're tagging along out of curiosity,\NI'd prefer you didn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.98,0:15:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.42,0:15:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinemann?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.22,0:15:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Could if be that you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.16,0:15:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,related to Director Heinemann, who was\Nmurdered at Eisler Memorial Hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.60,0:15:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.53,0:15:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,is the man who ruined my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the only one who can save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.72,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\an8}St. Jaromir Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.49,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,80,,{\i1}Kenzo Tenma, who has been taken{\i}\N{\i1}into custody in Prague...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}will be deported to Germany within{\i}\N{\i1}the next couple of days to stand trial.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.70,0:15:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He will be transferred to Düsseldorff{\i}\N{\i1}where the string of murders began.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.40,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After an interrogation...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.94,0:15:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the police are going to inspect{\i}\N{\i1}the crime scene with Dr. Tenma.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.44,0:15:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.87,0:15:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That man...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.21,0:15:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.81,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.38,0:16:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Suk, he's the man who saved your life.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.85,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's because of his emergency treatment that you're alive.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Tenma is also being accused{\i}\N{\i1}or crimes he did not commit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's in the same situation as you.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,The man who saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.39,0:16:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's also in the same situation as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're a detective, aren't you?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you're a detective....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then you have to calmly dissect the situation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you don't want to be betrayed anymore...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.41,0:16:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then start doubting the person{\i}\N{\i1}you want to doubt the least{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.85,0:16:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I have to get to Prague Station...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and talk with Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been looking for you, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.80,0:16:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Blazek...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.40,0:16:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Stransky...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:16:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.44,0:17:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to run anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.54,0:17:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We've put you through quite a bit of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.38,0:17:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been cleared of all charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.78,0:17:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter was delivered to the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.12,0:17:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.25,0:17:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a confession with the kinds of details...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,regarding the whole case that\Nonly the killer would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All the charges against you have been dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who sent the letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone by the name of Grimmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.53,0:17:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.83,0:17:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We've already put a warrant out for\NGrimmer as the prime suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay now, Suk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.61,0:17:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Zeman's murder, the\Ncommissioner's poisoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.98,0:17:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and the special task force murders...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.12,0:17:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,have now all been resolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.75,0:18:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where have you been, Lunge?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been calling your number all day!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.76,0:19:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I went out sightseeing for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Geez! Stop playing dumb!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.46,0:19:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Playing dumb?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Knock it off already!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet you've heard the news!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.37,0:19:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,About Dr. Tenma's arrest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.67,0:19:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations, Lunge.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You knew, right?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.18,0:19:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Tenma was hiding out in Prague.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good job Lunge.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the result of your thorough investigation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We contacted the Czech police immediately and{\i}\N{\i1}completed the deportation arrangements.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tenma will be transferred to Düsseldorf{\i}\N{\i1}tomorrow afternoon.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.33,0:19:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Since you're in charge of this case...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.16,0:19:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to personally supervise his transfer.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.93,0:19:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, you did a good job, Lunge.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.04,0:19:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Congratulations.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.50,0:19:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you assign it to someone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.01,0:19:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.17,0:19:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Prague is a nice place.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.45,0:19:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm still on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Lunge!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.68,0:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you saying?!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.85,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me see Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been telling you, you can't see him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.46,0:20:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't this country become a democracy
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.96,0:20:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenma is about to be deported back to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.57,0:20:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that happens, even if only for a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we wasted our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we came all the way to Prague...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.01,0:20:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Even just a quick look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.81,0:20:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When we interrogate someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,what kind of person do you think\Nis the toughest to crack?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone whose expression never changes.\Nregardless of the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone who doesn't say a word.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That kind of person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.52,0:21:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,A love letter from a monster to a beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.86,0:21:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like the draft for a novel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I've been watching you all this time."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.57,0:21:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"To eat up every bit of you."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.01,0:21:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"But instead, everything about you has devoured me."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I wonder what I look like to you,{\i}\N{\i1}who is collapsing into ruin."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"That which you left me, which is collapsing into ruin."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.65,0:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"You left me with such beautiful jewels."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.42,0:21:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The twins, who are like eternal life itself."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.73,0:21:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The greatest sin..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"is to take away a person's name."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Reclaim your name."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I return your name to you."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.60,0:22:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Your name is... Anna."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.37,0:22:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"I'm filled with sorrow now."{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.34,0:22:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Filled with sorrow..."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Filled with sorrow..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.42,0:22:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It exists...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.52,0:22:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The many people who died in that room...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.76,0:22:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.59,0:22:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A terrifying monster was born!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.74,0:22:29.45,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:34.30,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Ima kono seka de
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:39.50,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}wakaru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:43.38,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}mitsumeta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.33,0:22:45.64,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:50.48,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Anata no hitomi no
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:56.04,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}yasashisa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:59.86,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.89,0:22:39.50,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Gazing at what is known
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:43.38,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}now in this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:59.86,ED3,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Your eyes believe in kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:21.12,ED2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Make it home
